NORWEGIAN SEA.
ROCKETS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS IN PROGRESS UNTIL 30 DEC:
   A. WITHIN TWO MILES OF 69-18N 016-01E.
      BETWEEN 270 DEGREES AND 020 DEGREES.
   B. IN AREA BOUND BY
      69-50N 016-34E, 70-59N 015-20E,
      70-18N 012-02E, 69-22N 014-33E.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 31 DEC.
